游戏为[[開放世界|开放世界]]环境，玩家可自由探索。游戏世界设有多种环境，包括森林、河流和山脉<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/08/15/gamescom-2014-far-cry-4-glimpse-into-kyrat-trailer-rewind-theater|title=Gamescom 2014: Far Cry 4 Glimpse Into Kyrat Trailer Rewind Theatre|first=Tate|last=Fiebing|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2014-08-15|accessdate=2015-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924225339/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/08/15/gamescom-2014-far-cry-4-glimpse-into-kyrat-trailer-rewind-theater|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。为了让玩家更快地旅行，游戏添加了各种载具，包括越野车、卡车、水上交通工具如[[馬達快艇|快艇]]，玩家可在驾驶时进行射击。有些交通工具有自动驾驶功能，开启后内置的[[人工智能|人工智能]]将控制车辆的行动，从而使玩家专注于自己的目标<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-12-02-moving-targets-the-scattergun-politics-of-far-cry-4|title=Moving targets: the scattergun politics of Far Cry 4|first=Edwin|last=Evans-Thirlwell|date=2014-12-02|accessdate=2015-08-25|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905061106/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-12-02-moving-targets-the-scattergun-politics-of-far-cry-4|archive-date=2015-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。玩家还可以劫持其他车辆。游戏还引入了蜂鸣直升机等空中载具，使玩家在空中获得战术优势<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/games/far_cry_4/b/playstation4/archive/2014/06/11/taking-down-a-fortress-with-a-friend-in-far-cry-4.aspx|title=Taking Down A Fortress With A Friend In Far Cry 4|first=Matt|last=Bertz|work=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]|date=2014-06-11|accessdate=2015-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924144809/http://www.gameinformer.com/games/far_cry_4/b/playstation4/archive/2014/06/11/taking-down-a-fortress-with-a-friend-in-far-cry-4.aspx|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。降落伞、滑翔衣和攀爬钩爪可帮助玩家跨越悬崖以及快速导航<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2014/12/16/the-many-minor-missteps-of-far-cry-4/123608/|title=The Many (Minor) Missteps of Far Cry 4|first=Thomas|last=Elia|date=2014-12-16|accessdate=2015-08-25|work=[[Hardcore_Gamer|Hardcore Gamer]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924043705/http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2014/12/16/the-many-minor-missteps-of-far-cry-4/123608/|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本作部分情节发生于神秘幻境[[香格里拉|香格里拉]]，玩家将扮演凯拉特战士卡里纳格（Kalinag）与恶魔战斗。在香格里拉任务中会有一只受伤的白虎跟随玩家。玩家可以对白虎发出指令，令其攻击敌人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.engadget.com/2014/08/18/far-cry-4-crouching-tiger-hidden-blood-dragon/|title=Far Cry 4: Crouching tiger, hidden Blood Dragon|first=Ludwig|last=Kietzmann|work=[[Joystiq|Joystiq]]|date=2014-08-18|accessdate=2015-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924143912/http://www.engadget.com/2014/08/18/far-cry-4-crouching-tiger-hidden-blood-dragon/|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/08/14/gamescom-2014-5-reasons-far-cry-4-looks-like-a-trip-worth-taking|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|title=Gamescom 2014: 5 Reason Far Cry 4 Looks Like A Trip Worth Taking|first=Tristan|last=Oglivie|date=2014-08-14|accessdate=2015-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924225324/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/08/14/gamescom-2014-5-reasons-far-cry-4-looks-like-a-trip-worth-taking|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

游戏世界分为两部分：南凯拉特和北凯拉特。玩家一开始位于南凯拉特并可以随时自由探索，北凯拉特必须在完成一定的任务后才可解锁进入。在未解锁前游戏地图被一片迷雾覆盖，玩家在解放蒲甘·明控制的钟楼后，地图会逐渐打开，地图上的事物也会被标示<ref name="Tips">{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/tips-for-playing-far-cry-4-1661679705|title=Tips for playing Far Cry 4|date=2014-11-24|accessdate=2015-08-25|first=Yannick|last=LeJacq|work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150810124100/http://kotaku.com/tips-for-playing-far-cry-4-1661679705|archive-date=2015-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，这也有利于“黄金之路”扩大其势力。世界各地分布着由蒲甘·明控制的前哨，玩家可渗透之。四个较大的前哨，或者说堡垒，具有更强的防御和更完善的敌军组合。如果玩家成功解放了前哨，它们将成为快速旅行点，可在游戏世界之间快速导航，其他任务及支线也会随之解锁<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/10-ways-stay-alive-far-cry-4-deadly-world/|work=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]|title=10 ways to stay alive in Far Cry 4's deadly world|first=David|last=Roberts|date=2014-10-14|accessdate=2015-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924020729/http://www.gamesradar.com/10-ways-stay-alive-far-cry-4-deadly-world/|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏还有许多小任务，如解救人质、拆除炸弹和狩猎等。收集的动物皮可用于制作弹药袋、针剂袋等物品袋<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gamingbolt.com/far-cry-4-interview-world-size-crafting-side-quests-and-more|title=Far Cry 4 Interview: World Size, Crafting, Side Quests And More|first=Rashid|last=Sayed|date=2014-09-10|accessdate=2015-08-25|work=Gaming Bolt|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002190647/http://gamingbolt.com/far-cry-4-interview-world-size-crafting-side-quests-and-more|archive-date=2015-10-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vg1247.com/2014/10/06/far-cry-4-karma-chaos-kyrat/|title=Far Cry 4: karma and chaos in Kyrat|first=Matt|last=Martin|work=[[VG_247|VG 247]]|date=2014-10-06|accessdate=2015-08-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208074728/http://www.vg1247.com/2014/10/06/far-cry-4-karma-chaos-kyrat/|archivedate=2015-12-08}}</ref>。

与前作类似，游戏具有一定的[[電子角色扮演遊戲|角色扮演]]元素。玩家在完成任务、击杀敌人后可获得经验值，经验值可用来升级玩家的能力。游戏中的技能分为虎象两系，虎系技能专注于肉搏、武器和物理动作；而象系技能专注于生命值、治疗和制作各种针剂<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamersky.com/handbook/201411/490288_4.shtml |title=孤岛惊魂4 游戏系统指南 全要素图文解析 |publisher=[[游民星空|游民星空]] |date=2014-11-19 |accessdate=2015-11-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117141813/http://www.gamersky.com/handbook/201411/490288_4.shtml |archivedate=2015-11-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。各种随机事件和敌军遭遇贯穿整个游戏。例如，玩家可能会意外地被老鹰袭击、被车撞或目睹动物的捕食。玩家可通过帮助叛军“黄金之路”的成员以积累业报（Karma），如协助他们打败敌人或野生动物。业报积累后，玩家在购买新武器时会有折扣，并且可以在遇到困难时呼叫其成员来支援己方作战<ref name="PCTrailer" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-10-14-why-ajay-ghale-isnt-the-real-star-of-far-cry-4|title=Why Ajay Ghale isn't the real star of Far Cry 4|first=Aoife|last=Wilson|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2014-10-14|accessdate=2015-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907181857/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-10-14-why-ajay-ghale-isnt-the-real-star-of-far-cry-4|archive-date=2015-09-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。玩家还可以通过收集面具、撕掉宣传海报、转动[[轉經筒|转经筒]]来积累经验<ref name="Tips" />。游戏还设有竞技场模式，在此模式中玩家要与人类和动物战斗以获取额外的经验值和奖励<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/far-cry-4s-arena-mode-is-a-gladiator-style-humans-/1100-6422371/|title=Far Cry 4's Arena Mode Is a Gladiator-Style, Humans vs. Animals Affair|first=Eddie|last=Makuch|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|date=2014-09-17|accessdate=2015-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906190759/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/far-cry-4s-arena-mode-is-a-gladiator-style-humans-/1100-6422371/|archive-date=2015-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 多人 ===

