团队希望《孤岛惊魂4》中有像《孤岛惊魂3》“游戏中的游戏”的结构，所以设计了香格里拉任务<ref name="FarCry3.5"/>，它与凯拉特没有什么关联，但在游戏叙事中发挥了重要作用。在开发这一部分时，团队着重色彩的运用。他们希望《孤岛惊魂4》的艺术视野异于其他同类型的射击游戏。它最初被设计为一个小型开放世界，但因时间限制和开发人员之间创意的巨大分歧，最终此部分转变为线性设计。团队后来决定简化它，并重新将其构想为“古老、自然的世界”。香格里拉由五种不同的色调构成，主色调为金色，团队认为这会为幻境增加暖色调；同时，红色被大量运用，用以构建陌生的感觉以及与游戏的叙事相搭配；橙色用于交互，而白色代表世界的纯净；蓝色是香格里拉最后的色调，代表着危险与荣誉<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/features/2015/3/16/8219481/shangri-la-far-cry-4-artwork-gallery-gdc-2015|title=Painting Shangri-La|first=Dave|last=Tach|work=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|date=2015-03-16|accessdate=2015-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150812091615/http://www.polygon.com/features/2015/3/16/8219481/shangri-la-far-cry-4-artwork-gallery-gdc-2015|archive-date=2015-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

育碧承诺《孤岛惊魂4》多人元素将远超《孤岛惊魂3》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/far-cry-4-will-have-a-lot-more-multiplayer-than-far-cry-3/1100-6419681/|title=Far Cry 4 will have "a lot more multiplayer" than Far Cry 3|first=Eddie|last=Makuch|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|date=2014-05-16|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150904134739/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/far-cry-4-will-have-a-lot-more-multiplayer-than-far-cry-3/1100-6419681/|archive-date=2015-09-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一些因时间限制被《孤岛惊魂3》取消的元素将在《孤岛惊魂4》中得到添加，如多人合作模式“雇佣之枪”<ref name="VentureBeat interview"/>。它本来为独立模式，但后来被集成到主战役中<ref name="PolyE3"/>。游戏的竞争性多人模式允许玩家升级并通过不同的方式打败敌人。红色风暴娱乐吸收了玩家对于《孤岛惊魂3》多人游戏的反馈意见，并决定将车辆加入游戏中。团队选择了非对称结构模式，这样玩家可以在不同的比赛中有不同的体验，并使比赛变得更加混乱<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gametrailers.com/videos/iukn6b/far-cry-4-the-making-of-pvp--battles-of-kyrat-|title=Far Cry 4:The Making of PvP (Battles of Kyrat)|work=[[GameTrailers|GameTrailers]]|date=2014-11-04|accessdate=2015-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924122413/http://www.gametrailers.com/videos/iukn6b/far-cry-4-the-making-of-pvp--battles-of-kyrat-|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。开发商原本计划以女性作为玩家角色，但因动画问题而放弃<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-06-12-far-cry-4-almost-had-female-co-op-characters|title=Far Cry 4 "almost" had female co-op characters|first=Tom|last=Phillips|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2014-06-12|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150911001206/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-06-12-far-cry-4-almost-had-female-co-op-characters|archive-date=2015-09-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。育碧宣布拥有PlayStation 3和PlayStation 4版本的玩家将会获得“凯拉特之钥”（Keys to Kryat）。它允许拥有者为其他10名未拥有游戏的人提供密钥。获得密钥的玩家可加入邀请者的多人合作模式并可游玩两个小时<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.psu.com/News/24977/Far-Cry-4-PlayStation-exclusive-Keys-to-Kryat-offer-unlimited-sessions|title=Far Cry 4 PlayStation exclusive 'Keys to Kryat' offer 'unlimited sessions'|first=Simon|last=Sayers|work=[[PlayStation_Universe|PlayStation Universe]]|date=2014-10-20|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924082920/http://www.psu.com/News/24977/Far-Cry-4-PlayStation-exclusive-Keys-to-Kryat-offer-unlimited-sessions|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

{{Le|克里夫·马丁内兹| Cliff Martinez}}负责游戏的配乐工作，游戏共发布了两张包含30首游戏曲目的光盘版及一张额外添加15首曲目的豪华版。专辑在游戏发售之前发行，并得到了好评，特别是对尼泊尔传统乐器的使用与结合<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/11/03/composer-cliff-martinez-officially-working-on-far-cry-4-soundtrack|title=Composer Cliff Martinez Officially Working On Far Cry 4 Soundtrack|first=Lauren|last=Puga|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2014-11-03|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150917015210/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/11/03/composer-cliff-martinez-officially-working-on-far-cry-4-soundtrack|archive-date=2015-09-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===发行===
随着《孤岛惊魂3》在商业上获得成功，育碧把孤岛惊魂系列视为其最重要的品牌之一。2013年6月，育碧暗示续作正在开发中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/06/20/ubisoft-more-far-cry-games-are-coming|title=Ubisoft: More Far Cry Games Are Coming|first=Andrew|last=Goldfarb|date=2013-06-20|accessdate=2015-08-26|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924201807/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/06/20/ubisoft-more-far-cry-games-are-coming|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年10月3日，马丁内兹提到他正致力于游戏原声音乐的制作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.engadget.com/2013/10/08/drive-composer-cliff-martinez-mentions-work-on-far-cry-4/|title='Drive' composer Cliff Martinez mentions work on Far Cry 4|first=Mike|last=Suszek|work=[[Joystiq|Joystiq]]|date=2013-10-08|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924141949/http://www.engadget.com/2013/10/08/drive-composer-cliff-martinez-mentions-work-on-far-cry-4/|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年3月，游戏的设定及特性遭到泄露<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-03-20-far-cry-4-set-in-the-himalayas-has-ridable-elephants|title=Far Cry 4 set in the Himalayas, has ridable elephants|first=Tom|last=Phillips|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2014-03-21|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924135820/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-03-20-far-cry-4-set-in-the-himalayas-has-ridable-elephants|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年5月15日，《孤岛惊魂4》正式公布，第一个游戏画面于[[E3电子娱乐展|E3]] 2014放出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/05/15/far-cry-4-announced-for-2014|title=Far Cry 4 Announced for 2015|first=Mitch|last=Dyer|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2015-05-15|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150812004428/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/05/15/far-cry-4-announced-for-2014|archive-date=2015-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在游戏的艺术封面中，浅肤色的蒲甘·明把手放在一个深肤色的人的头上，这引起了争议和种族主义的指控。哈钦森后来澄清道，蒲甘·明并非白种人，而且封面中的另一个人也并非游戏主角<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/05/21/far-cry-4-creative-director-addresses-box-art-controversy|title=Far Cry 4 Creative Director Addresses Box Art Controversy|first=Lucy|last=O'Brien|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2014-05-20|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150815160021/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/05/21/far-cry-4-creative-director-addresses-box-art-controversy|archive-date=2015-08-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/far-cry-4-creative-director-comments-on-controversial-box-art/1100-6419759/|title=Far Cry 4 creative director comments on controversial box art|first=Chris|last=Pereira|date=2014-05-20|accessdate=2015-08-26|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150914014919/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/far-cry-4-creative-director-comments-on-controversial-box-art/1100-6419759/|archive-date=2015-09-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他还说大众对艺术封面的反应“令人不舒服”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-06-23-dont-judge-far-cry-4-by-its-cover-says-game-director?|title=Don't judge Far Cry 4 by its cover, says game director|first=Jeffery|last=Matulef|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2014-06-24|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150910235522/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-06-23-dont-judge-far-cry-4-by-its-cover-says-game-director|archive-date=2015-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

除了标准版外，游戏还有限量版发行。限量版提供额外的任务及武器鱼叉枪，预购游戏的玩家将免费获得此版本的升级<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.engadget.com/2014/10/03/far-cry-4-limited-edition-adds-extra-missions-bonus-monkeys/|title=Far Cry 4 Limited Edition adds extra missions, bonus monkeys|first=Danny|last=Cowan|work=[[Joystiq|Joystiq]]|date=2014-10-03|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924144138/http://www.engadget.com/2014/10/03/far-cry-4-limited-edition-adds-extra-missions-bonus-monkeys/|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏另有凯拉特版，包含收藏盒子、海报、杂志、凯拉特地图、蒲甘·明的小雕像以及限量版的额外任务<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/games/far_cry_4/b/playstation4/archive/2014/07/06/far-cry-4-kyrat-edition-includes-pagan-min-statue.aspx|title=Far Cry 4 Kyrat Edition Includes Pagan Min Statue|first=Kyle|last=Hilliard|work=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]|date=2014-07-06|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715095826/http://www.gameinformer.com/games/far_cry_4/b/playstation4/archive/2014/07/06/far-cry-4-kyrat-edition-includes-pagan-min-statue.aspx|archive-date=2014-07-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。玩家还可购买游戏的季票，它包含新的竞争性多人游戏模式、限量版的任务与新任务“注射器”以及另外两个追加下载内容<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/30-far-cry-4-season-pass-announced-includes-multip/1100-6423065/|title=$30 Far Cry 4 Season Pass Announced, Includes Multiplayer Mode and Yeti Missions|first=Eddie|last=Makuch|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|date=2014-10-20|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907064026/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/30-far-cry-4-season-pass-announced-includes-multip/1100-6423065/|archive-date=2015-09-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《孤岛惊魂4》于2014年11月18日在北美发行，11月20日在欧洲发行，11月21日在英国发行，覆盖[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]、[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]、[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]平台<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vg247.com/2014/05/15/far-cry-4-assassins-creed-unity-will-lead-ubisofts-company-performance-this-year/|title=Far Cry 4 release date announced for November on PC, current and last-gen platforms|first=Stephany|last=Nunneley|work=[[VG_247|VG 247]]|date=2014-05-15|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150927113819/http://www.vg247.com/2014/05/15/far-cry-4-assassins-creed-unity-will-lead-ubisofts-company-performance-this-year/|archive-date=2015-09-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏的PlayStation4、Xbox One和PC版本具有更高的视觉保真，如具有较高的纹理分辨率和更多的动物皮毛<ref name="DSInterview" />。游戏也支持可下载内容，第一个DLC“逃离杜尔格施监狱”（Escape From Durgesh Prison）添加了一个设定在战役期间的新任务，于2015年1月13日发布，支持单人或双人游玩<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.vg247.com/2015/01/13/far-cry-4s-escape-from-durgesh-prison-dlc-is-now-available/|title=Far Cry 4’s Escape from Durgesh Prison DLC is now available|first=Sherif|last=Saed|work=[[VG_247|VG 247]]|date=2015-01-13|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150910055335/http://www.vg247.com/2015/01/13/far-cry-4s-escape-from-durgesh-prison-dlc-is-now-available/|archive-date=2015-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/far-cry-4-permadeth-dlc-available-now/1100-6424617/|title=Far Cry 4 Permadeth DLC Available Now|first=Eddie|last=Makuch|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|date=2015-01-13|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905133154/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/far-cry-4-permadeth-dlc-available-now/1100-6424617/|archive-date=2015-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。“占领”（Overrun）DLC增加了新地图、载具以及竞争性多人游戏的新模式，于2015年2月10日登陆主机平台，2月12日登陆PC平台<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/02/10/far-cry-4-overrun-dlc-out-now|title=Far Cry 4 Overrun DLC Out Now|first=Michael|last=Martin|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2015-02-10|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150731145914/http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/02/10/far-cry-4-overrun-dlc-out-now|archive-date=2015-07-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。贺克豪华包（Hurk Deluxe Pack）增加了一些任务和武器，于2015年1月28日发布<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vg247.com/2015/01/28/far-cry-4-hurk-deluxe-dlc-now-available/|title=Far Cry 4 Hurk Deluxe DLC now available|first=Brenna|last=Hillier|work=[[VG_247|VG 247]]|date=2015-01-28|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150910032804/http://www.vg247.com/2015/01/28/far-cry-4-hurk-deluxe-dlc-now-available/|archive-date=2015-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最后一个追加下载内容“雪人谷”（Valley of the Yetis）具有全新的地区及任务，同样支持单人或双人合作模式。雪人谷DLC分别于2015年3月10日及11日在北美和欧洲发布<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/far-cry-4-dlc/|title=Far Cry 4 Valley of the Yetis DLC hits in March|work=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]|date=2015-02-28|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924082744/http://www.gamesradar.com/far-cry-4-dlc/|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

